Tell Gina that you know someone
who wants to meet her.

rows.label: qev065502_MSG0003

Not that it's anything to brag about, but I'm pretty no-
nonsense. I say what I think. Some of the folks at the
bar say they like that about me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065502_MSG0004
rows.name:

Suffice to say it's a happening little spot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065502_MSG0005
rows.name:
And no, I'm not seeing anyone right now.
Plenty of guys ask, but never the right ones.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065502_MSG0006
rows.name: What, you know a guy who wants to meet me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065502_MSG0007
rows.name:
Heh. I tell you, it's tough being this irresistible.
How many does that make this month?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065502_MSG0008
rows.name:
But yeah, I'm happy to meet up, at least. No promises,
but you never know. He could be the one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065502_MSG0009
rows.name:
He's not half-bad. And having a catch like that be
interested in you feels pretty good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065502_MSG0010
rows.name:
He's a hunk, but also... I don't know. Pure, maybe?
If I'm not careful, it'll be me falling for him here![ST:wait ]
